<head><meta charset="utf-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"><base href="&mvte:global:basehref;"><title>Identifying Genuine Sinister Diesel Parts</title><meta name="description" content="Use six practical checks to identify genuine Sinister Diesel products and avoid counterfeit or unauthorized parts."><mvt:if expr="g.useDevResources EQ 1"><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list_dev" /><mvt:else><mvt:item name="head" param="css_list" /></mvt:if><mvt:item name="head" param="head_tag" /></head>
<body class="single-column"><mvt:item name="hdft" param="global_header" /><mvt:item name="hdft" param="header" />
<main class="sd2-cp sd2-genuine"><section class="sd2-policy__hero"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><nav class="sd2-policy__breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="&mvte:urls:SFNT:auto;">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Genuine parts</span></nav><p class="sd2-cp__eyebrow">Brand protection / Buyer guide</p><h1>Verify the<br>real thing.</h1><p>Six practical checks help distinguish genuine Sinister Diesel products from counterfeit, altered and unsupported parts.</p><div class="sd2-cp__actions"><a class="sd2-cp__button sd2-cp__button--primary" href="#genuine-checks">Open the checklist</a><a class="sd2-cp__button" href="authorized-resellers.html">Authorized resellers</a></div></div></section>
	<div class="sd2-cp__signal"><div><span>01</span><strong>Inspect the part</strong></div><div><span>02</span><strong>Verify the seller</strong></div><div><span>03</span><strong>Protect the purchase</strong></div></div>
	<section class="sd2-cp__section" id="genuine-checks"><div class="sd2-cp__shell"><div class="sd2-cp__section-head"><div><p class="sd2-cp__label">Authenticity checklist</p><h2>Look beyond the color.</h2></div><p>Color alone is not proof. Use the part mark, packaging, product code, seller and purchase record together.</p></div><mvt:item name="readytheme" param="contentsection( 'identifying-genuine-sinister-parts' )" /></div></section>
